title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Roundhouse
description:
A true all-mountain rockered machine built to support larger feet, while delivering performance peak to parking lot; a high-end daily cruiser that provides the quickness and power you need for 12 rounds of hard driving, all-terrain, mixed-condition fun.
To learn more about the Roundhouse visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/roundhouse/
